---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Invierto Ya - Experto en Inversiones y Educación Financiera"
  description="Aprende a invertir de forma inteligente con Invierto Ya. Estrategias de inversión, análisis de mercado y educación financiera para construir tu futuro económico."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-lg">
      <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">
          <h1>Invierto Ya</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-6">
          <a href="#newsletter" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Newsletter</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Blog</a>
          <a href="/sobre-mi" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Sobre Mí</a>
          <a href="/contacto" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Contacto</a>
        </div>
        <button class="md:hidden">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Newsletter Section - Primera prioridad -->
    <section id="newsletter" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            El primer paso para Invertir <br> <strong>¡Empieza Aquí!</strong>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
Sumate a mi newsletter semanal y recibí ideas claras, consejos simples y herramientas para que empieces a invertir con confianza.          </p>
          
          <!-- Brevo Newsletter Form -->
          <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <div class="sib-form" style="text-align: center;">
              <div id="sib-form-container" class="sib-form-container">
                <div id="error-message" class="sib-form-message-panel" style="font-size:16px; text-align:left; font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#661d1d; background-color:#ffeded; border-radius:3px; border-color:#ff4949;max-width:540px; display: none;">
                  <div class="sib-form-message-panel__text sib-form-message-panel__text--center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" class="sib-icon sib-notification__icon">
                      <path d="M256 40c118.621 0 216 96.075 216 216 0 119.291-96.61 216-216 216-119.244 0-216-96.562-216-216 0-119.203 96.602-216 216-216m0-32C119.043 8 8 119.083 8 256c0 136.997 111.043 248 248 248s248-111.003 248-248C504 119.083 392.957 8 256 8zm-11.49 120h22.979c6.823 0 12.274 5.682 11.99 12.5l-7 168c-.268 6.428-5.556 11.5-11.99 11.5h-8.979c-6.433 0-11.722-5.073-11.99-11.5l-7-168c-.283-6.818 5.167-12.5 11.99-12.5zM256 340c-15.464 0-28 12.536-28 28s12.536 28 28 28 28-12.536 28-28-12.536-28-28-28z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="sib-form-message-panel__inner-text">
                      No hemos podido validar su suscripción.
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div id="success-message" class="sib-form-message-panel" style="font-size:16px; text-align:left; font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#085229; background-color:#e7faf0; border-radius:3px; border-color:#13ce66;max-width:540px; display: none;">
                  <div class="sib-form-message-panel__text sib-form-message-panel__text--center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" class="sib-icon sib-notification__icon">
                      <path d="M256 8C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 464c-118.664 0-216-96.055-216-216 0-118.663 96.055-216 216-216 118.664 0 216 96.055 216 216 0 118.663-96.055 216-216 216zm141.63-274.961L217.15 376.071c-4.705 4.667-12.303 4.637-16.97-.068l-85.878-86.572c-4.667-4.705-4.637-12.303.068-16.97l8.52-8.451c4.705-4.667 12.303-4.637 16.97.068l68.976 69.533 163.441-162.13c4.705-4.667 12.303-4.637 16.97.068l8.451 8.52c4.668 4.705 4.637 12.303-.068 16.97z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="sib-form-message-panel__inner-text">
                      ¡Gracias por suscribirte! 🎉 📬 Acabamos de enviarte un email para confirmar tu suscripción. Revisá tu bandeja de entrada y, si no lo ves en unos minutos, verificar la carpeta de spam.
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div id="sib-container" class="sib-container--large sib-container--vertical" style="text-align:center; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,1); max-width:540px; border-radius:12px; border-width:0px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); direction:ltr; margin: 0 auto;">
                  <form id="sib-form" method="POST" action="https://2b71d996.sibforms.com/serve/MUIFALLISobCuB0MdRVhjPsUm-Pu1bHil0UM7KzHUJbj4O-H0kKPmQMlLM6r2wp-YGAJRRUKDRNBgsPZhJxDcl9fgxqbiiEuwSZzZ9gmC_E617QqHM-SswzSUDhO9mYmNq3blRXBEXPShQrI-SdVQXegv7H3rrqcych8UZLCBkzTJITdWCrw-GvfdSSMbkGztlUTPJ_4ct_4w4H1" data-type="subscription">
                    <div style="padding: 20px;">
                      <div class="space-y-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="sib-input sib-form-block">
                          <div class="form__entry entry_block">
                            <div class="form__label-row">
                              <div class="entry__field">
                                <input class="input w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent" maxlength="200" type="text" id="NOMBRE" name="NOMBRE" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Tu Nombre" data-required="true" required />
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <label class="entry__error entry__error--primary" style="font-size:14px; text-align:left; font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#661d1d;">
                            </label>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="sib-input sib-form-block">
                          <div class="form__entry entry_block">
                            <div class="form__label-row">
                              <div class="entry__field">
                                <input class="input w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent" type="email" id="EMAIL" name="EMAIL" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Tu Email" data-required="true" required />
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <label class="entry__error entry__error--primary" style="font-size:14px; text-align:left; font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#661d1d;">
                            </label>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="sib-captcha sib-form-block mb-4">
                        <div class="form__entry entry_block">
                          <div class="form__label-row">
                            <script is:inline>
                              function handleCaptchaResponse() {
                                var event = new Event('captchaChange');
                                var captchaElement = document.getElementById('sib-captcha');
                                if (captchaElement) {
                                  captchaElement.dispatchEvent(event);
                                }
                              }
                            </script>
                            <div class="g-recaptcha sib-visible-recaptcha flex justify-center" id="sib-captcha" data-sitekey="6LebKFcrAAAAAFGlmKECj9lZN7FGhkD84w-viSE-" data-callback="handleCaptchaResponse" style="direction:ltr"></div>
                          </div>
                          <label class="entry__error entry__error--primary" style="font-size:14px; text-align:left; font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#661d1d;">
                          </label>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="sib-form-block" style="text-align: center">
                        <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center justify-center" form="sib-form" type="submit">
                          <svg class="icon clickable__icon progress-indicator__icon sib-hide-loader-icon mr-2" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
                            <path d="M460.116 373.846l-20.823-12.022c-5.541-3.199-7.54-10.159-4.663-15.874 30.137-59.886 28.343-131.652-5.386-189.946-33.641-58.394-94.896-95.833-161.827-99.676C261.028 55.961 256 50.751 256 44.352V20.309c0-6.904 5.808-12.337 12.703-11.982 83.556 4.306 160.163 50.864 202.11 123.677 42.063 72.696 44.079 162.316 6.031 236.832-3.14 6.148-10.75 8.461-16.728 5.01z" fill="currentColor" />
                          </svg>
                          🚀 UNIRME AHORA
                        </button>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <input type="text" name="email_address_check" value="" class="input--hidden">
                    <input type="hidden" name="locale" value="es">
                  </form>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          

          
          <!-- Redes Sociales -->
          <div class="mt-8">
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm mb-4">📱 Sígueme en mis redes sociales:</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
              <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@invierto.ya" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-30 p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 group">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M19.59 6.69a4.83 4.83 0 0 1-3.77-4.25V2h-3.45v13.67a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-5.2 1.74 2.89 2.89 0 0 1 2.31-4.64 2.93 2.93 0 0 1 .88.13V9.4a6.84 6.84 0 0 0-1-.05A6.33 6.33 0 0 0 5 20.1a6.34 6.34 0 0 0 10.86-4.43V7a8.16 8.16 0 0 0 4.77 1.52v-3.4a4.85 4.85 0 0 1-1-.43z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="sr-only">TikTok</span>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@inviertoya" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-30 p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 group">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="sr-only">YouTube</span>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/invierto.ya/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-30 p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 group">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12.017 0C8.396 0 7.989.013 7.041.048 4.928.048 3.335 1.653 3.335 3.766 3.335 4.714 3.335 5.121 3.335 8.742v6.551c0 2.089 1.593 3.682 3.706 3.682h9.551c2.113 0 3.706-1.593 3.706-3.682V8.742C20.298 5.121 20.298 4.714 20.298 3.766 20.298 1.653 18.705.048 16.592.048H12.017zm0 1.44c2.136 0 2.389.007 3.232.043.78.035 1.204.166 1.486.275.373.145.64.319.92.599.28.28.453.546.598.92.11.281.24.705.275 1.485.037.843.043 1.096.043 3.231s-.006 2.389-.043 3.232c-.035.78-.166 1.203-.275 1.485a2.47 2.47 0 0 1-.599.919c-.28.28-.546.453-.92.598-.281.11-.705.24-1.485.276-.843.036-1.096.042-3.231.042s-2.389-.006-3.232-.042c-.78-.036-1.203-.166-1.485-.276a2.478 2.478 0 0 1-.92-.598 2.48 2.48 0 0 1-.6-.92c-.109-.281-.24-.705-.275-1.485-.036-.843-.041-1.096-.041-3.23 0-2.134.005-2.389.041-3.232.036-.78.166-1.204.276-1.486.145-.373.319-.64.599-.92.28-.28.546-.453.92-.598.282-.11.705-.24 1.485-.276.738-.034 1.024-.044 2.515-.045v.002zm4.988 1.328a.96.96 0 1 0 0 1.92.96.96 0 0 0 0-1.92zm-4.27 1.122a4.109 4.109 0 1 0 0 8.217 4.109 4.109 0 0 0 0-8.217zm0 1.441a2.667 2.667 0 1 1 0 5.334 2.667 2.667 0 0 1 0-5.334z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
              </a>
              <a href="https://x.com/invierto_ya" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-30 p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 group">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="sr-only">X (Twitter)</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          Construye tu <span class="text-blue-600">Futuro Financiero</span> con Estrategias Inteligentes
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Experto en inversiones con más de 10 años de experiencia. Te ayudo a tomar decisiones financieras informadas y a crear un portfolio diversificado que genere resultados consistentes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="#newsletter" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            📧 Suscríbete al Newsletter</a>
          <a href="#servicios" class="border border-blue-600 text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
            Ver Mis Servicios</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section id="servicios" class="bg-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">
          Servicios de Inversión
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Análisis de Mercado</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Análisis técnico y fundamental detallado para identificar oportunidades de inversión con alto potencial de retorno.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Gestión de Portfolio</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Construcción y optimización de carteras de inversión personalizadas según tu perfil de riesgo y objetivos financieros.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Educación Financiera</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Cursos y mentorías personalizadas para que aprendas a invertir de forma autónoma y tomes decisiones informadas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">
            Sobre Invierto Ya
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            Con más de una década de experiencia en los mercados financieros, he ayudado a cientos de personas a construir su libertad financiera a través de estrategias de inversión inteligentes y educación financiera práctica.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">500+</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">Clientes Satisfechos</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">10+</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">Años de Experiencia</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">95%</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">Tasa de Éxito</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contacto" class="bg-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">
          ¿Listo para Invertir?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Agenda una consulta gratuita de 30 minutos para discutir tus objetivos financieros y descubrir cómo puedo ayudarte a alcanzarlos.
        </p>
        <button class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          Agendar Consulta Gratuita
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
